ring days on which the Dow declined, while only 8 occurred during days on which it advanced. None of the top 20 occurred before the year 2015.\n\nDuring the [[2020 stock market crash]], nine of the top ten positions occurred during a span of three weeks between March 2, 2020 and March 20, 2020.\n<div class=\"mw-collapsible mw-shown\">\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:right\"\n! Rank\n! Date\n! Close\n! Day high\n! Day low\n! Point swing\n! Net change\n|-\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |1\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |2020-03-13\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |23,185.62\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |23,189.76\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |21,285.37\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |1,904.39\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |+1,985.00\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |2\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |2020-03-12\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |21,200.62\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |22,837.95\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |21,154.46\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |1,683.49\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |\u22122,352.60\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |3\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |2020-03-16\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |20,188.52\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |21,768.28\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |20,116.46\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |1,651.82\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |\u22122,997.10\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |4\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |2018-02-05\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |24,345.75\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |25,520.53\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |23,923.88\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |1,596.65\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |\u22121,175.21\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |5\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |2020-03-18\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |19,898.92\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |20,489.33\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |18,917.46\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |1,571.87\n| style=\"background:#f66;\" |\u22121,338.46\n|-\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |6\n| style=\"background:#9f6;\" |2020-03-17\n| style=\"b